<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-fuel-poverty-advisory-group> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Fuel Poverty Advisory Group ( FPAG ) is now called the Committee on Fuel Poverty . FPAG advised on the effectiveness of policies aimed at reducing fuel poverty, and encouraged greater co-ordination across the organisations working to reduce fuel poverty."@en .
